<BaseLayout
  title="Sodium Benzoate - Ingredient Safety Profile"
  description="Learn about sodium benzoate in cat litter: what it is, safety concerns for cats, and better alternatives for litter box care."
  ogImage="/og/ingredients-sodium-benzoate.png"
